<p>
	Dave, John, and Pilot Pete come together on this Sunday afternoon to chat about wrangling in Notification Center, managing (and deleting!) &#8220;recent recipients&#8221; in iOS mail, understanding Java versions, managing the Launchpad and much, much more!</p>
